extend layout
  
block content
  .page-header.text-center
    h1(style='font-weight: 700;') You're subscribing to Cheese!
    p.lead You will be billed for $#{cheeseAmount} monthly, starting today.
    p.lead Subscriptions allows us to better gauge our resources and optimize our servers to produce the fastest, more reliable experience.
    a(href="/cancel", style="display:inline-block; margin-right:2em;")
      button.btn.btn-primary Nevermind...
    form.form-inline(method="post", style="display:inline-block;")
      button.btn.btn-warning(type="submit") Sounds great!
    p.text(style="margin-top:1em;")
      if user
        strong You are logged in! Your contribution will be public. Logout if you wish to remain anonymous.
      else
        strong You aren't logged in! This contribution will be anonymous, and the Cheese will not be attached to an account.